# Implementation Plan - Instant FAQ Generator Professionalization

The goal is to elevate the current prototype into a polished, professional-grade application suitable for a high-end agency portfolio. We will focus on code structure, "premium" UI/UX, and project maintainability.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Tech Stack Decision**: We will stick to **Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS** for the frontend to keep it lightweight and aligned with the current Vercel setup, but we will significantly upgrade the **Design System** to match "Ogilvy" standards (premium, dark mode, smooth animations).
>
> **Dependency Management**: We will introduce a [package.json](file:///Users/georgegayl/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/instant-faq-generator/package.json) to manage tooling (Prettier, ESLint) even if the runtime dependencies are minimal.

